@startuml
title Manage Users Activity Diagram

start
:1. Open user management;
:2. Search/select user;
:3. View user details;

if (4. Action required?) then (Yes)
  :5. Edit/Suspend/Delete user;
  :6. Update database;
endif

:7. Display updated status;
stop

note right
Activity Description:
1. Admin opens management module.
2. User is searched or selected.
3. Details displayed.
4. Admin decides action.
5. Account modified or removed.
6. Database updated.
7. Updated status shown.
end note
@enduml